{"tid":904374,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"好想知台灣人其實係咪好難先接觸到世界 剩係活係自己國家","createTime":"2018-11-16T09:49:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-16T11:45:22.000Z","uid":215700,"like":21,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"32cf189aec81e73d93751efc5127ef6dc684f675","tid":904374,"uid":215700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T09:49:09.000Z","msg":"人工 普通大學生起薪低到仆街 <br />\n一萬港紙都未必有 係台灣本土生活就話物價低無問題啫 但平時要儲幾耐先有錢去次旅行<br />\n<br />\n好啦你話依個年代識上網就見識到好多野<br />\n偏偏班台灣人十個有六七個都唔識/唔願意接觸英文<br />\n識幾個台灣大學生 廿幾歲人從來唔會上外國網 <br />\n無中譯就唔睇外國片<br />\n<br />\n香港男仔再差 同人傾計點都有文有路咩都識少少 唔會比人覺得係鄉下仔 台灣男仔連有鬼妹鬼佬問路都唔識答<br />\n<br />\n台灣人其實係咪除左扑野就咩都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a82a1432e0d3a74ca2026521fc1e1d793de3f71e","tid":904374,"uid":156592,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T09:51:18.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"25dd38ad956f1058104f5a98a721555f0b1db85f","tid":904374,"uid":2148,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T09:53:28.000Z","msg":"其實日本都係咁<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17ad138b2a5b96ad5b318509c245f5fe69b1e653","tid":904374,"uid":89931,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T09:55:56.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過只係因為香港係國際大都市而特別唔同"},{"pid":"ea0a98b78cf2256015c7f42be0cc10091fbafce8","tid":904374,"uid":171310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25dd38ad956f1058104f5a98a721555f0b1db85f","tid":904374,"uid":2148,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T09:53:28.000Z","msg":"其實日本都係咁<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T09:56:14.000Z","msg":"真係好似日本"},{"pid":"00c18cd120b4ca557fd9e28bad27fa71899d5e27","tid":904374,"uid":208722,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T09:56:46.000Z","msg":"香港男仔再差 同人傾計點都有文有路咩都識少少<br />\n<br />\n再睇睇連登<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7797a6d4bccd84082109f116659e3b2756f96d9a","tid":904374,"uid":208722,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T09:57:39.000Z","msg":"踩人哋打飛機唔會令自己成長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f857a47c36a9d4ddeecbc0beec187cd85f0f6241","tid":904374,"uid":131725,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T09:59:30.000Z","msg":"講到係香港個d好好咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c710327877f683f1535e7dfb9287df89ec1e58c","tid":904374,"uid":141782,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T09:59:56.000Z","msg":"英文又差睇唔明外國網<br />\n台灣傳媒又凈係識報埋d on9 新聞<br />\n有咩辦法唔on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adb7409e7e223347d847886e0a9b6c930f6896dd","tid":904374,"uid":32699,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T10:00:04.000Z","msg":"不知幾多youtube中譯片都係台仔整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家如果國家自給自足到 <br />\n國民的確未必須要咁多國際視野 就好似日本咁<br />\n不過我都覺得普遍台仔思想上比較唔成熟"},{"pid":"e6d2c5ac2166037c9344646f65f02c8a1ce1be75","tid":904374,"uid":118999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T10:02:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實日本都係咁<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n日本有能力玩自閉，台灣就真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d4cc363f32e71a7b9c65d5a3787e40055b7d9ae","tid":904374,"uid":177578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T10:04:26.000Z","msg":"所有國家既窮人都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch